  }\n\n  .am-circle-box {\n    background: #0047AB;\n    border-radius: 2px;\n    padding: 28px;\n    margin-top: 38px;\n  }\n\n  .am-circle-kicker {\n    font-family: 'Jost', Arial, sans-serif;\n    font-size: 15px;\n    letter-spacing: 3px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: rgba(253,246,227,0.6);\n    margin-bottom: 8px;\n  }\n\n  .am-circle-title {\n    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;\n    font-size: 24px;\n    color: #fdf6e3;\n    margin-bottom: 8px;\n  }\n\n  .am-circle-text {\n    font-family: 'Jost', Arial, sans-serif;\n    font-size: 13px;\n    line-height: 1.7;\n    color: rgba(253,246,227,0.72);\n    margin-bottom: 22px;\n  }\n\n  .am-circle-form {\n    display: flex;\n    max-width: 480px;\n  }\n\n  .am-circle-form input {\n    flex: 1;\n    min-width: 0;\n    padding: 12px 16px;\n    font-family: 'Jost', Arial, sans-serif;\n    font-size: 13px;\n    background: #fdf6e3;\n    color: #1a1a1a;\n    border: none;\n    border-radius: 2px 0 0 2px;\n  }\n\n  .am-circle-form button {\n    padding: 12px 20px;\n    font-family: 'Jost', Arial, sans-serif;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    letter-spacing: 2px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: #0047AB;\n    background: #fdf6e3;\n    border: none;\n    border-left: 1px solid rgba(0,71,171,0.15);\n    border-radius: 0 2px 2px 0;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    white-space: nowrap;\n  }\n\n  .am-circle-privacy {\n    font-family: 'Jost', Arial, sans-serif;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    color: #fdf6e3;\n    margin-top: 12px;\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width: 768px) {\n    .am-philosophy-layout {\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n    }\n\n    .am-philosophy-images {\n      position: static;\n      flex-direction: row;\n      gap: 10px;\n    }\n\n    .am-philosophy-caption {\n      display: none;\n    }\n\n    .am-philosophy-frame {\n      padding: 32px 22px;\n    }\n\n    .am-philosophy-title {\n      font-size: 28px;\n      letter-spacing: 3px;\n    }\n\n    .am-philosophy-subtitle {\n      font-size: 20px;\n      margin-bottom: 30px;\n    }\n\n    .am-philosophy-lead {\n      font-size: 20px;\n    }\n\n    .am-philosophy-body {\n      font-size: 17px;\n    }\n\n    .am-circle-form {\n      flex-direction: column;\n      gap: 8px;\n    }\n\n    .am-circle-form input,\n    .am-circle-form button {\n      width: 100%;\n      border-radius: 2px;\n    }\n  }\n<\/style>\n\n<div class=\"am-philosophy-page\">\n  <div class=\"am-philosophy-layout\">\n\n    <aside class=\"am-philosophy-images\">\n      <div>\n        <div class=\"am-philosophy-image-wrap\">\n          <img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0974\/7480\/6097\/files\/500px-Marc_Chagall_9_9_17_-lacma_-theater__40584496951.jpg?v=1776450819\" alt=\"Marc Chagall, Fantasies for the Stage\" loading=\"lazy\">\n        <\/div>\n        <div class=\"am-philosophy-caption\">Marc Chagall<br>Fantasies for the Stage<br>Photo: Sharon Mollerus \/ CC BY 2.0<\/div>\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div>\n        <div class=\"am-philosophy-image-wrap\">\n          <img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0974\/7480\/6097\/files\/250px-Sophie_Taeuber-Arp__1889_1943__Composition__1931.png?v=1776855678\" alt=\"Sophie Taeuber-Arp, Composition, 1931\" loading=\"lazy\">\n        <\/div>\n        <div class=\"am-philosophy-caption\">Sophie Taeuber-Arp<br>Composition, 1931<br>Muzeum Sztuki, Łódź<\/div>\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div>\n        <div class=\"am-philosophy-image-wrap\">\n          <img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0974\/7480\/6097\/files\/250px-Blaise_cendrars__fernad_leger__locandina_per_la_fin_du_monde__1919_1.jpg?v=1776452377\" alt=\"Fernand Léger, La Fin du Monde, 1919\" loading=\"lazy\">\n        <\/div>\n        <div class=\"am-philosophy-caption\">Fernand Léger<br>La Fin du Monde, 1919<br>Photo: Francesco Bini \/ CC BY-SA 4.0<\/div>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/aside>\n\n    <main class=\"am-philosophy-frame\">\n      <div class=\"am-philosophy-content\">\n\n        <h1 class=\"am-philosophy-title\">Our Philosophy<\/h1>\n        <div class=\"am-philosophy-subtitle\">Less, But Better<\/div>\n\n        <p class=\"am-philosophy-body\">Most jewellery is designed to match most things. It sits quietly, coordinates politely, then disappears. There is a whole industry built around this kind of discretion, and it produces beautiful, forgettable things in enormous quantities.<\/p>\n\n        <p class=\"am-philosophy-body\">Atelier Modernista was born from an opposite impulse: a love of jewellery that has genuine presence. The reference points here are not other jewellery brands - they are Sophie Taeuber-Arp’s colour-richness and geometry, Chagall’s flying lovers, Léger’s vivid lettering, Le Brocquy’s <em>Táin<\/em> illustrations, and Jane South’s geometric paper sculptures.<\/p>\n\n        <p class=\"am-philosophy-body\">We built Atelier Modernista on a few simple convictions: buying less but buying better; that colour is everyone’s friend; and that jewellery made by artists, chosen with rigour, is worth more than almost anything produced at scale.<\/p>\n\n        <blockquote class=\"am-philosophy-quote\">\n          \"Creativity is more than just being different. Anybody can plan weird; that's easy. What's hard is to be as simple as Bach. Making the complicated simple, awesomely simple - that's creativity.\" \n          <cite>Charles Mingus<\/cite>\n        <\/blockquote>\n\n        <p class=\"am-philosophy-body\">Our Edits are always kept small. We would rather show you ten things we believe in completely than a hundred things we think you might like. The pieces we offer are chosen because they do something special - something that makes us feel more vivid when we wear them.<\/p>\n\n<p class=\"am-philosophy-body\">Each piece has presence, and each has earned its place. Our jewellery range is small and ever-rotating, meaning you can regularly find new ideas at play.<\/p>\n\n        <p class=\"am-philosophy-body\">Presence doesn't need drama. Just a surprise dart of colour, an unusual texture, or a cobalt richness that makes you feel interesting things are ahead.<\/p> \n\n<p class=\"am-philosophy-body\">Creative elegance - the kind that's vivid and entirely yours.<\/p>\n\n<p class=\"am-philosophy-body\">Warmest wishes,<\/p>\n\n<p class=\"am-philosophy-body\">Antonia + Team Atelier Modernista<\/p>\n\n        <section class=\"am-circle-box\">\n          <div class=\"am-circle-kicker\">The Atelier Circle<\/div>\n          <div class=\"am-circle-title\">Stay in the edit.<\/div>\n          <div class=\"am-circle-text\">Join The Atelier Circle for exclusive early access to sales and new arrivals, and occasional Collector’s Notes. Unsubscribe any time.<\/div>\n\n          {% form 'customer', class: 'am-circle-form' %}\n            <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"contact[tags]\" value=\"newsletter,NW3CIRCLE\">\n            <input type=\"email\" name=\"contact[email]\" placeholder=\"Your email address\" required autocomplete=\"email\">\n            <button type=\"submit\">Join the Circle<\/button>\n          {% endform %}\n\n          <div class=\"am-circle-privacy\">Your details are kept private.<\/div>\n        <\/section>\n\n      <\/div>\n    <\/main>\n\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>","color_scheme":"","padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":52}}},"order":["main","177462817241fe8f78","1776202336a9220bf4","custom_liquid_pNMYAC","custom_liquid_CPeKki"]}